<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br><font face="arial">I’ve been unable to reach you and so have been unable to provide you with a business insurance quote.</font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If you are&nbsp;<b>interested in proceeding with a quote</b>,&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">reply with the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively you can give me a ring on&nbsp;</span></font><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">.<br></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white;"><br></font><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}<br></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></font></span><font style="font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
